QUALIFICATION: Yamaguti (1959), not Fischthal (1953; in fact 1954) as appears in Schmidt (1986), erroneously listed this species in Bialovarium, most probably just as misplacement because of the same initials as Biacetabulum (there is no reason for accommodation in Bialovarium).
